data.description: Location on the Truckee River in the River Park Community. Views from the rear of the home.  This is a quiet neighborhood with close access to the Truckee River and numerous hiking and biking trails. Lakemont built home is very well maintained by original owner, 2 bedrooms 2 baths, and a den which can easily be turned into a 3rd bedroom. Built ins for TVs, Books and knickknacks. 3 car garage is spacious with cupboards and overhead shelving.  Walk to the trails, fish on the river, and easy access to downtown
